               <p>Q. Tell us what articles of yours are there - A. There are four pieces of sattin ribbon, and one piece of sarsnet, they were in them boxes, they were produced before the Alderman, they are worth five pounds, at the least value.</p>
               <p>GUILTY, aged 19.</p>
